title: Iman Shumpert In The Trap! W  DCYoungFly, Karlous Miller & Chico Bean | Ep. 255
itunes:title: Iman Shumpert In The Trap! W  DCYoungFly, Karlous Miller & Chico Bean | Ep. 255
description:
NBA champion Iman Shumpert pulled up the podcast dolo to talk about how he's living his hoop dreams and how the coronavirus has impacted NBA life. Plus he shares some stories of competing and winning with stars like Lebron James and Kobe Bryant. GET SOME MERCH! https://85apparelco.com/ DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean post up with the 6'6 nba star and they go down too many hilarious rabbit holes of conversation. Plus Iman explains how Teyana Taylor collaborate creatively on making music and art. Plus he talks about his new music project he's working on and he breaks down his history as an artist. Sit back and learn something from one the coolest players in the game!
